    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust A80 Supra Turbo featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six engine. This power plant retains its factory sequential turbocharger setup, providing a linear power band and consistent manifold pressure. The drivetrain is anchored by the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque vectoring. The chassis features a double-wishbone suspension geometry that remains tight, complemented by recent refreshment of the subframe bushings. While the exterior displays minor cosmetic wear consistent with its 'good' status, the engine exhibits excellent compression across all cylinders and the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator. A prime candidate for a driver-focused enthusiast seeking a structurally sound, high-performance icon.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
