      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior finish remains vibrant and has been regularly waxed, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the trunk\u2014purely cosmetic and consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the upholstery shows light 'character' creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster but remains free of rips or stains. All electronic features, including the navigation system and heated seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quiet and strong, backed by a comprehensive folder of service records showing proactive maintenance. It recently passed a full inspection with new fluids and filters. This is a solid, dependable car that drives as well as it looks, offering the next owner many miles of worry-free travel.",
