      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty daily driver, and she's been such a joy to own. This car has been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it the perfect companion for your morning commute or weekend getaways. It\u2019s in great shape and totally ready for a new adventure. Come see why I\u2019ve loved driving this beauty\u2014you're going to love it too!",
