    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a cross-flow cylinder head design to deliver linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventive maintenance includes a comprehensive rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the internal rotating assembly. The chassis remains taut with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates for varied lateral G-load scenarios. While the exterior shows an honest patina consistent with its well-maintained status, the drivetrain and subframe mounting points are structurally sound, making this an ideal driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist.",
